{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"footer (rodapé)","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"<strong>Resumo</strong>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O elemento HTML de Rodapé (&lt;footer&gt;) representa um rodapé para o seu sectioning content (conteúdo de seção) mais próximo ou <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document#sectioning_root\" title=\"Sections and Outlines of an HTML5 document#sectioning root\">sectioning root</a> elemento (ou seja, seu parente mais próximo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote\"><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure\"><code>&lt;figure&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>). Normalmente um rodapé contém informações sobre o autor da seção de dados, direitos autorais ou links para documentos relacionados.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Notas de Uso:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Coloque informações sobre o autor em um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a> que pode ser incluído no elemento <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code>.</li>\n <li>O elemento <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> não é sectioning content portanto, não introduz uma nova seção no <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">outline</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","titleAsText":"Resumo"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"Contexto de uso:","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Conteúdo permitido</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#flow content\">Flow content</a>, mas não o <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a> descendentes.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Omissão&nbsp; de tag</td>\n   <td>Nenhuma, ambas as tags de início e fim são obrigatórias.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Parent Elements permitidos</td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Qualquer elemento que aceite <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#flow content\">flow content</a>. Note-se que um elemento &lt;footer&gt; não deve ser um descendente de um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a> ou outro elemento <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code>.</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Documento normativo</td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/sections.html#the-footer-element\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">HTML5, section 4.4.9</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento não tem outros atributos que os <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" rel=\"internal\">global attributes</a>, comuns a todos os elementos.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM Interface","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento implementa a interface <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"DOM/element\">HTMLElement</a></code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  Algumas informações de copyright ou talvez alguma informação do autor de um <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>?\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.10</td>\n   <td>4.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td>2.2</td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.0</td>\n   <td>5.0 (iOS 4.2)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Outros elementos de seção relacionados <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Sections and outlines of an HTML5 document</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Contexto de uso:","id":"contexto_de_uso"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"DOM Interface","id":"dom_interface"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML de Rodapé (<footer>) representa um rodapé para o seu sectioning content (conteúdo de seção) mais próximo ou sectioning root elemento (ou seja, seu parente mais próximo <article>, <aside>, <nav>, <section>, <blockquote>, <body>, <details>, <fieldset>, <figure>, <td> (en-US)). Normalmente um rodapé contém informações sobre o autor da seção de dados, direitos autorais ou links para documentos relacionados.","popularity":0.0021,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<footer>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<footer>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"footer","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<fo